 Graphs to feed your active local agent enclaves with synchronized contextual context mapping.\"\n251 |           : \"Construct automated data ingestion pipelines using semantic chunkers to process legacy PDFs, SOPs, and manual logs securely.\";\n252 |       } else if (dim.id === \"process\") {\n253 |         rec = avg >= 2.5\n254 |           ? \"Deploy passive supervisor nodes to constantly measure multi-agent DAG latency bottlenecks and optimize step executions.\"\n255 |           : \"Digitize core manual workflows and document decision state boundaries before modeling autonomous handoffs.\";\n256 |       } else if (dim.id === \"talent\") {\n257 |         rec = avg >= 2.5\n258 |           ? \"Adopt Platform-as-a-Product structures to let internal engineering teams spin up isolated, pre-governed agents independently.\"\n259 |           : \"Roll out GFF AI Academy modules across target divisions to improve prompt literacy and reduce digital-transition friction.\";\n260 |       } else if (dim.id === \"governance\") {\n261 |         rec = avg >= 2.5\n262 |           ? \"Implement zero-retention boundary policies and cryptographically sign execution steps for high-integrity regulatory audits.\"\n263 |           : \"Install automated input/output security middleware to detect and redact sensitive customer identifiers (PII) at the edge.\";\n264 |       } else if (dim.id === \"techstack\") {\n265 |         rec = avg >= 2.5\n266 |           ? \"Introduce GFF Orchestration Gateways to dynamically route model calls based on cost, latency thresholds, and residency rules.\"\n267 |           : \"Transition operational workloads from public cloud API keys to private cloud enclaves or local containerized serving structures.\";\n268 |       } else if (dim.id === \"leadership\") {\n269 |         rec = avg >= 2.5\n270 |           ? \"Co-develop custom proprietary model adapters and pioneer topologies in collaborative syncs with GFF Labs.\"\n271 |           : \"Secure protected, multi-year CAPEX reserves to insulate early-stage pilot models from short-term financial fluctuations.\";\n272 |       } else {\n273 |         rec = avg >= 2.5\n274 |           ? \"Design full-duplex human-agent queues allowing operators and active supervisor bots to collaboratively resolve complex tasks.\"\n275 |           : \"Adopt a federated Center of Excellence (CoE) to streamline compliance clearances and standardize deployable templates.\";\n276 |       }\n277 | \n278 |       return { ...dim, avg, status, statusStyle, rec };\n279 |     });\n280 | \n281 |     // Dynamic Strengths mapping based on actual scores\n282 |     const strengths = dimensionBreakdowns\n283 |       .filter(d => d.avg >= 2.5)\n284 |       .map(d => {\n285 |         let desc = \"\";\n286 |         if (d.id === \"strategy\") desc = \"High alignment ensures capital allocation tracks execution metrics closely.\";\n287 |         else if (d.id === \"data\") desc = \"Clean unstructured semantic storage structures simplify embedding enclaves.\";\n288 |         else if (d.id === \"process\") desc = \"Clear manual decision handoffs prevent deadlocks during agent execution loops.\";\n289 |         else if (d.id === \"talent\") desc = \"Internal prompt literacy minimizes transitional engineering blockages.\";\n290 |         else if (d.id === \"governance\") desc = \"Existing boundary structures satisfy core regulatory redaction standards.\";\n291 |         else if (d.id === \"techstack\") desc = \"Private server architectures support fully containerized local execution environments.\";\n292 |         else if (d.id === \"leadership\") desc = \"Calculated risk tolerance empowers engineering to pilot proprietary adaptors.\";\n293 |         else desc = \"Centralized templates standardise pipelines and facilitate sandbox promotion.\";\n294 |         \n295 |         return { name: d.name, desc };\n296 |       });\n297 | \n298 |     // Dynamic Risks mapping based on actual scores\n299 |     const risks = dimensionBreakdowns\n300 |       .filter(d => d.avg < 2.5)\n301 |       .map(d => {\n302 |         let desc = \"\";\n303 |         if (d.id === \"strategy\") desc = \"Fragmented ad-hoc prioritizing risks budget drift and redundant departmental tooling.\";\n304 |         else if (d.id === \"data\") desc = \"Legacy database structures introduce hallucination variables and slow context ingestion.\";\n305 |         else if (d.id === \"process\") desc = \"High manual latency and unmapped workflows choke autonomous multi-agent scaling.\";\n306 |         else if (d.id === \"talent\") desc = \"Lack of dedicated prompt modeling capacity slows platform integration.\";\n307 |         else if (d.id === \"governance\") desc = \"Standard API endpoints with open access keys risk accidental telemetry leaks.\";\n308 |         else if (d.id === \"techstack\") desc = \"Third-party model dependencies expose enterprise systems to latency fluctuations.\";\n309 |         else if (d.id === \"leadership\") desc = \"Risk-averse capital allocation parameters threaten competitive multi-year stagnation.\";\n310 |         else desc = \"Siloed delivery channels delay software deployment cycles past 6 months.\";\n311 | \n312 |         return { name: d.name, desc };\n313 |       });\n314 | \n315 |     // Recommended GFF pathway details\n316 |     let recommendedPath = {\n317 |       id: \"garage\",\n318 |       name: \"GFF Garage\",\n319 |       badge: \"Rapid Sandbox & Pilot Scaling\",\n320 |       color: \"text-[#E4000F]\",\n321 |       borderColor: \"border-[#E4000F]/30\",\n322 |       glowBg: \"bg-[#E4000F]/5\",\n323 |       desc: \"Perfect for organizations in early strategic stages. GFF Garage provides rapid, risk-insulated Web Sandboxes and prompt literacy modules. Start by modeling isolated workflows, validating key decision barriers, and securing dedicated executive sponsorship without extensive capital exposure.\",\n324 |       focus: \"Ideation, Pilot Scoping, Basic Sandboxing, and Executive Alignment.\"\n325 |     };\n326 | \n327 |     if (percentage >= 85) {\n328 |       recommendedPath = {\n329 |         id: \"operate\",\n330 |         name: \"GFF Operate\",\n331 |         badge: \"Continuous Symbiosis & Autonomy\",\n332 |         color: \"text-[#00FF9D]\",\n333 |         borderColor: \"border-[#00FF9D]/30\",\n334 |         glowBg: \"bg-[#00FF9D]/5\",\n335 |         desc: \"Designed for world-class digital grids. GFF Operate launches full-duplex human-agent collaborative queues, deploys active security supervisor nodes to constantly inspect schemas at runtime, and runs continuous model guardrails to prevent token drift at 99.9% telemetry success.\",\n336 |         focus: \"Full-Duplex Handoffs, Real-Time Guardrails, Dynamic Optimization, and Active Supervisors.\"\n337 |       };\n338 |     } else if (percentage >= 60) {\n339 |       recommendedPath = {\n340 |         id: \"factory\",\n341 |         name: \"GFF Factory\",\n342 |         badge: \"Production Scaling & Fleet Orchestration\",\n343 |         color: \"text-[#3B82F6]\",\n344 |         borderColor: \"border-[#3B82F6]/30\",\n345 |         glowBg: \"bg-[#3B82F6]/5\",\n346 |         desc: \"Tailored for organizations with proven data context and private cloud enclaves. GFF Factory coordinates high-velocity agent fleets, deploys advanced semantic orchestration gateways, and standardizes continuous deployment (CI/CD) of secure agentic microservices across systems.\",\n347 |         focus: \"Multi-Agent Fleet Coordination, Routing Gateways, and Continuous Compliance Integration.\"\n348 |       };\n349 |     } else if (percentage >= 35) {\n350 |       recommendedPath = {\n351 |         id: \"foundry\",\n352 |         name: \"GFF Foundry\",\n353 |         badge: \"Contextual Enclaves & Secure Ingestion\",\n354 |         color: \"text-[#E5A93C]\",\n355 |         borderColor: \"border-[#E5A93C]/30\",\n356 |         glowBg: \"bg-[#E5A93C]/5\",\n357 |         desc: \"Optimized for bridging the gap between isolated scripts and standardized platforms. GFF Foundry constructs enterprise-grade private cloud enclaves, implements Context Knowledge Graphs, and sets up secure vector cache servers to ingest legacy repositories cleanly.\",\n358 |         focus: \"Contextual Databases, Sovereign VPC Boundaries, Model Adapters, and Secure Gateways.\"\n359 |       };\n360 |     }\n361 | \n362 |     const nextActions = [\n363 |       \"Launch a local GFF Zero-Trust Sandbox session to safely trace sample multi-system agentic handoffs.\",\n364 |       \"Conduct a structured diagnostic scan of structured and unstructured context repositories to identify vector database prerequisites.\",\n365 |       \"Sync with GFF Labs to explore custom proprietary model adapters designed for strict local data retention rules.\",\n366 |       \"Generate an automated Topological Blueprint and draft an Algorithmic SOW to establish operational milestones.\"\n367 |     ];\n368 | \n369 |     return { percentage, tierName, tierColor, borderAccent, commentary, dimensionBreakdowns, strengths, risks, recommendedPath, nextActions };\n370 |   };\n371 | \n372 |   const report = showResult ? calculateResults() : null;\n373 | \n374 |   // Local-only handlers\n375 |   const handleCopyReport = () => {\n376 |     if (!report) return;\n377 |     const dimensionText = report.dimensionBreakdowns.map((d: any) => \n378 |       `- ${d.name}: ${d.avg}/4.0 (${d.status})\\n  Recommendation: ${d.rec}`\n379 |     ).join(\"\\n\");\n380 |     const strengthsText = report.strengths.map((s: any) => `- ${s.name}: ${s.desc}`).join(\"\\n\");\n381 |     const risksText = report.risks.map((r: any) => `- ${r.name}: ${r.desc}`).join(\"\\n\");\n382 |     const pathText = `Recommended GFF Pathway: ${report.recommendedPath.name}\\n${report.recommendedPath.desc}`;\n383 | \n384 |     const reportMarkdown = `\n385 | # GFF AI READINESS ASSESSMENT REPORT\n386 | Generated on: ${new Date().toLocaleDateString()}\n387 | Security Context: LOCAL SECURED TELEMETRY\n388 | \n389 | ## OVERALL READINESS SCORE: ${report.percentage}%\n390 | Maturity Band: ${report.tierName}\n391 | \n392 | ## KEY METRIC DIAGNOSIS\n393 | ${dimensionText}\n394 | \n395 | ## KEY STRENGTHS\n396 | ${strengthsText || \"None identified with average score >= 2.5.\"}\n397 | \n398 | ## DETECTED RISKS\n399 | ${risksText || \"None identified with average score < 2.5.\"}\n400 | \n401 | ## STRATEGIC GFF PATHWAY\n402 | ${pathText}\n403 | \n404 | ---\n405 | CONFIDENTIALITY NOTICE: This report was compiled locally in a zero-retention environment and is for directional planning only. No outcomes are guaranteed.\n406 |     `.trim();\n407 | \n408 |     navigator.clipboard.writeText(reportMarkdown);\n409 |     setCopied(true);\n410 |     setTimeout(() => setCopied(false), 2000);\n411 |   };\n412 | \n413 |   const handleExportArchive = () => {\n414 |     if (!report) return;\n415 |     const payload = {\n416 |       timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),\n417 |       score: report.percentage,\n418 |       maturity: report.tierName,\n419 |       answers,\n420 |       dimensionBreakdowns: report.dimensionBreakdowns.map((d: any) => ({\n421 |         id: d.id,\n422 |         name: d.name,\n423 |         score: d.avg,\n424 |         status: d.status,\n425 |         recommendation: d.rec\n426 |       })),\n427 |       strengths: report.strengths,\n428 |       risks: report.risks,\n429 |       path: report.recommendedPath,\n430 |       security: \"LOCAL VPC COMPLIANT\"\n431 |     };\n432 | \n433 |     const dataStr = \"data:text/json;charset=utf-8,\" + encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify(payload, null, 2));\n434 |     const downloadAnchor = document.createElement('a');\n435 |     downloadAnchor.setAttribute(\"href\", dataStr);\n436 |     downloadAnchor.setAttribute(\"download\", `gff_ai_readiness_report_${report.percentage}pct.json`);\n437 |     document.body.appendChild(downloadAnchor);\n438 |     downloadAnchor.click();\n439 |     downloadAnchor.remove();\n440 |     setSaved(true);\n441 |     setTimeout(() => setSaved(false), 2000);\n442 |   };\n443 | \n444 |   // Helper arrays for Native SVG Radar Chart\n445 |   const getRadarCoordinates = (dimensionBreakdowns: any[]) => {\n446 |     const center = 150;\n447 |     const radius = 95;\n448 |     return dimensionBreakdowns.map((res, i) => {\n449 |       const angleRad = (i * 45 - 90) * (Math.PI / 180);\n450 |       const factor = res.avg / 4.0;\n451 |       const r = factor * radius;\n452 |       const x = center + r * Math.cos(angleRad);\n453 |       const y = center + r * Math.sin(angleRad);\n454 |       return { x, y, name: res.shortName, score: res.avg, color: res.color, id: res.id };\n455 |     });\n456 |   };\n457 | \n458 |   const getGridOctagons = () => {\n459 |     const center = 150;\n460 |     const radius = 95;\n461 |     const levels = [0.25, 0.5, 0.75, 1.0];\n462 |     return levels.map((level) => {\n463 |       const points = Array.from({ length: 8 }).map((_, i) => {\n464 |         const angleRad = (i * 45 - 90) * (Math.PI / 180);\n465 |         const r = level * radius;\n466 |         const x = center + r * Math.cos(angleRad);\n467 |         const y = center + r * Math.sin(angleRad);\n468 |         return `${x},${y}`;\n469 |       }).join(\" \");\n470 |       return { points, levelLabel: level * 4 };\n471 |     });\n472 |   };\n473 | \n474 |   const getRadarSpokes = () => {\n475 |     const center = 150;\n476 |     const radius = 95;\n477 |     return Array.from({ length: 8 }).map((_, i) => {\n478 |       const angleRad = (i * 45 - 90) * (Math.PI / 180);\n479 |       const x = center + radius * Math.cos(angleRad);\n480 |       const y = center + radius * Math.sin(angleRad);\n481 |       return { x1: center, y1: center, x2: x, y2: y };\n482 |     });\n483 |   };\n484 | \n485 | \n486 |   return (\n487 |     <ToolPageShell showContact={!showResult}>\n488 |       <AnimatePresence mode=\"wait\">\n489 |         {/* COMPILED LOADING SCREEN */}\n490 |         {isCompiling && (\n491 |           <motion.div\n492 |             key=\"compiling\"\n493 |             initial={{ opacity: 0 }}\n494 |             animate={{ opacity: 1 }}\n495 |             exit={{ opacity: 0 }}\n496 |             className=\"min-h-[550px] flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-16 text-center space-y-8\"\n497 |           >\n498 |             <div className=\"relative w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center\">\n499 |               <div className=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-full border-2 border-[#009DFF]/20 animate-ping\" />\n500 |               <div className=\"absolute inset-2 rounded-full border border-[#00FF9D]/30 animate-pulse\" />\n501 |               <div className=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#030306] border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg\">\n502 |                 <svg className=\"w-6 h-6 text-[#009DFF] animate-spin\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n503 |                   <circle className=\"opacity-25\" cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth=\"4\" />\n504 |                   <path className=\"opacity-75\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M4 12a8 8 0 018-8V0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12h4zm2 5.291A7.962 7.962 0 014 12H0c0 3.042 1.135 5.824 3 7.938l3-2.647z\" />\n505 |                 </svg>\n506 |               </div>\n507 |             </div>\n508 |             <div className=\"space-y-2 max-w-lg\">\n509 |               <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest block\">TELEMETRY SECURE SCAN</span>\n510 |               <p className=\"text-white text-base font-semibold h-12 flex items-center justify-center leading-relaxed\">\n511 |                 {COMPILING_MESSAGES[compilingStep]}\n512 |               </p>\n513 |             </div>\n514 |             <div className=\"w-64 h-1 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden relative\">\n515 |               <div \n516 |                 className=\"h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#009DFF] to-[#00FF9D] transition-all duration-300\"\n517 |                 style={{ width: `${((compilingStep + 1) / COMPILING_MESSAGES.length) * 100}%` }}\n518 |               />\n519 |             </div>\n520 |           </motion.div>\n521 |         )}\n522 | \n523 |         {/* ACTIVE DIAGNOSTIC RUNNER */}\n524 |         {!isCompiling && !showResult && (\n525 |           <motion.div\n526 |             key=\"diagnostics\"\n527 |             initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 15 }}\n528 |             animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}\n529 |             exit={{ opacity: 0, y: -15 }}\n530 |             className=\"space-y-8\"\n531 |           >\n532 |             {/* Header section */}\n533 |             <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-6\">\n534 |               <div className=\"space-y-2 max-w-3xl\">\n535 |                 <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest block\">\n536 |                   BUILD-WITH-GFF // INTERACTIVE DIAGNOSTIC\n537 |                 </span>\n538 |                 <h1 className=\"text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight leading-none\">\n539 |                   Sovereign AI <span className=\"text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#009DFF] via-white to-[#00FF9D]\">Readiness Assessor</span>\n540 |                 </h1>\n541 |                 <p className=\"text-white/50 text-xs font-light leading-relaxed\">\n542 |                   Evaluate your organization’s strategic alignments, data pipeline security, process bottlenecks, governance compliance, and technology parameters. Establish a certified maturity baseline before scheduling agentic deployments.\n543 |                 </p>\n544 |               </div>\n545 |               <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030306]/90 min-w-[200px] flex items-center justify-between gap-4 font-mono\">\n546 |                 <div>\n547 |                   <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 block uppercase\">BUFFER SYNC</span>\n548 |                   <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-[#00FF9D]\">GATEWAY {answeredQuestionsCount} / {totalQuestions} READY</span>\n549 |                 </div>\n550 |                 <div className=\"text-xl font-extrabold text-white\">\n551 |                   {progressPercent}%\n552 |                 </div>\n553 |               </div>\n554 |             </div>\n555 | \n556 |             {/* Main panel layout */}\n557 |             <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-start\">\n558 |               {/* Left Column: Nav list of dimensions */}\n559 |               <div className=\"lg:col-span-3 space-y-4\">\n560 |                 <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030306]/90 space-y-3\">\n561 |                   <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-2\">\n562 |                     <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider block\">SEGMENT GATEWAYS</span>\n563 |                   </div>\n564 |                   <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n565 |                     {DIMENSIONS.map((dim, idx) => {\n566 |                       const done = isDimensionComplete(dim);\n567 |                       const count = getDimensionAnsweredCount(dim);\n568 |                       const isCurrent = idx === activeDimensionIndex;\n569 |                       \n570 |                       return (\n571 |                         <button\n572 |                           key={dim.id}\n573 |                           type=\"button\"\n574 |                           onClick={() => {\n575 |                             setValidationError(null);\n576 |                             setActiveDimensionIndex(idx);\n577 |                           }}\n578 |                           className={`w-full p-2.5 rounded-lg border text-left flex items-center justify-between transition-all ${\n579 |                             isCurrent \n580 |                               ? \"bg-white/[0.03] border-white/10 text-white\" \n581 |                               : \"bg-transparent border-transparent text-white/50 hover:text-white/90 hover:bg-white/[0.01]\"\n582 |                           }`}\n583 |                         >\n584 |                           <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 min-w-0\">\n585 |                             <span \n586 |                               className=\"p-1 rounded-md border flex-shrink-0\" \n587 |                               style={{ \n588 |                                 color: isCurrent ? dim.color : \"inherit\", \n589 |                                 borderColor: isCurrent ? `${dim.color}35` : \"rgba(255,255,255,0.05)\"\n590 |                               }}\n591 |                             >\n592 |                               {getDimensionIcon(dim.id)}\n593 |                             </span>\n594 |                             <span className=\"text-xs font-bold truncate tracking-tight\">{dim.name}</span>\n595 |                           </div>\n596 |                           <div className=\"font-mono text-[9px] flex-shrink-0 text-white/40\">\n597 |                             {done ? (\n598 |                               <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D] font-bold\">✓</span>\n599 |                             ) : count > 0 ? (\n600 |                               <span>{count}/3</span>\n601 |                             ) : (\n602 |                               <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/10\" />\n603 |                             )}\n604 |                           </div>\n605 |                         </button>\n606 |                       );\n607 |                     })}\n608 |                   </div>\n609 |                 </div>\n610 | \n611 |                 <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030306]/80 text-xs text-white/50 space-y-2\">\n612 |                   <div className=\"h-1 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\n613 |                     <div className=\"h-full bg-[#009DFF] transition-all duration-300\" style={{ width: `${progressPercent}%` }} />\n614 |                   </div>\n615 |                   <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[9px] font-mono\">\n616 |                     <span>OVERALL COMPILATION STATUS</span>\n617 |                     <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{progressPercent}%</span>\n618 |                   </div>\n619 |                 </div>\n620 |               </div>\n621 | \n622 |               {/* Center Column: Questions form */}\n623 |               <div className=\"lg:col-span-6 space-y-6\">\n624 |                 <div className=\"p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030306]/95 space-y-6\">\n625 |                   <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n626 |                     <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n627 |                       <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-[#009DFF] border border-white/10 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold\">\n628 |                         SECTOR {activeDimensionIndex + 1} OF {DIMENSIONS.length}\n629 |                       </span>\n630 |                       {isDimensionComplete(activeDimension) && (\n631 |                         <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-[#00FF9D]/10 text-[#00FF9D] border border-[#00FF9D]/20 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold\">\n632 |                           GATE COMPLETE\n633 |                         </span>\n634 |                       )}\n635 |                     </div>\n636 |                     <h2 className=\"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight mt-2 text-white\" style={{ color: activeDimension.color }}>\n637 |                       {activeDimension.name}\n638 |                     </h2>\n639 |                     <p className=\"text-white/50 text-xs mt-1.5 font-light leading-relaxed\">\n640 |                       {activeDimension.desc